| Backend | Node.js + Express.js |
| Base de datos | PostgreSQL (AWS RDS) |
| Caché | Redis (AWS ElastiCache) |
| Autenticación | Amazon Cognito |
| Hosting frontend | AWS S3 + CloudFront |
| Contenedores | Docker + AWS ECS Fargate |

